<h1>Intro to ChemSpider API</h1>

<p>Welcome to web of <a href="http://www.chemspider.com/AboutServices.aspx">ChemSpiderâ€™s Web Services API</a>.  The API taps into over 600 chemistry related database sources for synthesizing all your chemistry related applications.  You can use both SOAP, HTTP query, and REST protocols to search by and access information. The API is mainly split into four main categories:</p>

<ul>
    <li><a href="http://www.chemspider.com/Search.asmx">General Search API</a></li>
