        <li>Chemical format conversion</li>
    </ul>
</ul>

<p>ChemSpider's web API is elastic enough that it provides both synchronous and asynchronous functions, whereby one can check the status of their search compilation before sending, or send as soon as possible.  Given it's breadth, this How-To will dabble through  both types of functions, the four chemistry categories, as well as the REST and SOAP methods using implementations in JavaScript.  Before thinking about flying through this web, try getting registered with their web security token shown on the next page, or you might just get stuck, like a fly.  If you do consider building a full-fledged app, give ChemSpidera talk about allowing cross-origin access and Subscription Services.</p>
